{"text_id":142197,"tokens":["The"," facial"," action"," coding"," system"," (","FAC","S",")"," has"," gained"," popularity"," in"," recent"," years"," as"," a"," tool"," for"," detecting"," and"," measuring"," emotional"," responses","."," However",","," when"," considering"," its"," implementation"," in"," a"," classroom"," setting",","," several"," drawbacks"," and"," limitations"," must"," be"," considered",".","\n\n","One"," of"," the"," primary"," concerns"," with"," using"," FAC","S"," in"," a"," classroom"," is"," the"," potential"," for"," inaccuracy"," in"," data"," collection","."," The"," system"," relies"," on"," a"," trained"," r","ater"," to"," manually"," code"," the"," facial"," movements",","," which"," can"," be"," a"," time","-","consuming"," and"," subjective"," process","."," Moreover",","," the"," complexity"," of"," the"," system"," means"," that"," even"," a"," small"," mistake"," by"," the"," r","ater"," can"," significantly"," impact"," the"," accuracy"," of"," the"," data","."," This"," level"," of"," subjectivity"," raises"," questions"," about"," the"," reliability"," and"," general","izability"," of"," the"," results",","," which"," could"," potentially"," undermine"," the"," validity"," of"," any"," ensuing"," conclusions",".","\n\n","Furthermore",","," concerns"," about"," privacy"," and"," data"," protection"," also"," arise"," when"," using"," FAC","S"," in"," a"," classroom"," setting","."," Facial"," recognition"," technology"," is"," inherently"," intrusive",","," capturing"," sensitive"," information"," about"," students","'"," emotional"," responses",","," which"," could"," be"," potentially"," embarrassing"," or"," off","-","putting"," for"," them","."," Additionally",","," as"," students","'"," facial"," expressions"," may"," reveal"," more"," about"," their"," emotional"," state"," than"," they"," intend",","," this"," technology"," could"," potentially"," breach"," confidentiality"," and"," disclose"," sensitive"," information"," about"," students","'"," mental"," health"," or"," personal"," struggles",".","\n\n","Another"," significant"," limitation"," of"," using"," FAC","S"," in"," a"," classroom"," setting"," is"," the"," considerable"," cost"," associated"," with"," implementing"," and"," maintaining"," it","."," The"," system"," requires"," extensive"," training"," of"," rat","ers",","," detailed"," documentation",","," and"," specialized"," software",","," which"," can"," be"," a"," significant"," financial"," burden"," on"," already","-","strained"," educational"," budgets","."," This"," could"," result"," in"," a"," disproportion","ate"," allocation"," of"," resources",","," diverting"," funds"," away"," from"," other"," essential"," programs"," and"," initiatives"," crucial"," to"," student"," learning",".","\n\n","In"," conclusion",","," while"," the"," facial"," action"," coding"," system"," may"," offer"," valuable"," insights"," into"," emotional"," responses",","," its"," use"," in"," a"," classroom"," setting"," is"," not"," without"," its"," drawbacks","."," The"," potential"," for"," inaccuracy",","," privacy"," concerns",","," and"," significant"," cost"," make"," it"," necessary"," to"," carefully"," weigh"," the"," benefits"," of"," implementing"," this"," technology"," against"," these"," limitations","."," As"," educators",","," we"," must"," prioritize"," the"," well","-","being"," and"," dignity"," of"," our"," students",","," ensuring"," that"," any"," methodologies"," we"," employ"," respect"," their"," privacy",","," dignity",","," and"," autonomy",","," while"," also"," providing"," the"," most"," effective"," and"," beneficial"," learning"," experiences","."],"sub_source":"outfox","model":"llama3-8b","label":1}